content.rendered:
Directed by Duniya Vijay

Written by Maasthi Upparahalli

Cast Duniya Vijay(Salaga). Dhananjaya(ACP Samrat). Sanjana Anand(Sanjana). Neenasam Ashwath(SI Ashwath). Achyuth Kumar(Police Commissioner).Yash Shetty. Shrestha(Kenda). Cockroach Sudhi(Savithri (as Sudhir))

Language Kannada

Producers K.P. Srikanth. Duniya Vijay.

Production Venus Entertainers
